        public void createStaff()
        Randomly generate the role, gender, first name and last name of each of the staffs. Staff ID will be given accordingly to order. Staff ID 1 to 3 are designated Managers Staff ID 4 to 6 are designated Chefs Staff ID 6 to 20 are designated Waiters.
